Map: de_Pipeline_beta3 by Marshall

Terrorist Objectives:
Site A: Detonate a bomb near the pipeline.
Site B: Infiltrate the city and detonate a bomb in the plaza.

Counter-terrorist Objectives:
Defend against terrorist attack.  Prevent terrorists from planting explosives.
